Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:41.72,0:48:42.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:43.40,0:48:45.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}你从来没有问过他是谁，他是做什么的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:47.92,0:48:50.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}内芙拉  我这样跟你说吧……
