Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.72,0:49:50.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:50.36,0:49:51.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}那天晚上我真的很害怕
