Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:56.04,0:49:58.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}但你永远不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:58.76,0:50:02.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}你永远不知道别人会突然想起什么
