Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:14.20,0:51:15.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}这些年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.52,0:51:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}那真是我肩上的重担
