Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:26.28,0:51:27.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我永远不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:28.88,0:51:31.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}他来自哪里？去了哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.44,0:51:38.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-那警察从哪里来的？-警察？什么警察？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.60,0:51:41.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}那个给我做陈述的警察  第二天早上他跟我说了话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:42.44,0:51:43.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}他来自哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.44,0:51:47.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-警察吗？-是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.20,0:51:50.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}应该是从伊斯坦布尔来的  我没记住他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:50.76,0:51:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}他很年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.76,0:51:55.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}如果有照片，我也许可以认出他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.64,0:52:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:26.24,0:52:27.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:28.12,0:52:32.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}这是我欠你的钱  都还清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:33.60,0:52:35.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我做完你的脏活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:36.76,0:52:37.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:39.60,0:52:41.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}告诉我结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:42.12,0:52:43.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}告诉我你会放我走
