Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:48.84,0:52:51.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}你所做的事会不会不再萦绕在你心头吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.24,0:52:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我为了这些钱杀了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:54.80,0:52:56.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}哦，菲鲁兹
