Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.04,0:54:34.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}不，这样很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.32,0:54:39.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}关掉音乐！关掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:40.00,0:54:42.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-别挡我  -发生了什么事？
