Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.00,0:54:59.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-快出去  大叔！快走！-你以为你在做什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.72,0:55:03.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-回来，臭婊子！-把他们赶出去！快把他们赶出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:04.16,0:55:05.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}快走，你愁啥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:05.84,0:55:07.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}滚蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:07.60,0:55:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-他们这个月没有交税！-去尼玛的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:10.08,0:55:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}你有什么遗愿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:12.48,0:55:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我还真有，你能怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.68,0:55:18.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-快来人帮帮他  -闭嘴
