Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.24,0:55:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}不用担心  这不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:28.16,0:55:30.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}没办法  除此之外  我玩得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.84,0:55:34.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}我很生气，我没对那些混蛋说些什么
