Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:50.64,0:55:53.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}谢谢你所做的一切  晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.44,0:55:55.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.16,0:56:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}-这人穿的什么衣服？-他看起来很荒谬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.16,0:56:32.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}你们是黑手党的人吗？
